"title": "4366: stones",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4366: stones",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Pieces of rock, used extensively for building.</p>\n<h2>Stones used in building</h2>\n<h3>The temple in Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:17-1Kgs5:18\">1KI 5:17–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:14-1Kgs6:18\">1KI 6:14–6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:36\">1KI 6:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:9-1Kgs7:121\">1KI 7:9–7:121</a>CH <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:2\">22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14\">1CH 22:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:2\">1CH 29:2</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:3-2Kgs22:7\">2KI 22:3–22:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:8-2Chr34:11\">2CH 34:8–34:11</a> <em>repairing the temple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:1-Ezra6:4\">EZR 6:1–6:4</a> <em>rebuilding the temple after the exile</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:1-Matt24:2\">MAT 24:1–24:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:1-Mark13:2\">MRK 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:5-Luke21:6\">LUK 21:5–21:6</a> <em>Jesus Christ prophesies the temple's destruction.</em></p>\n<h3>Other references to building with stone</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:1-Gen11:3\">GEN 11:1–11:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:39-Lev14:45\">LEV 14:39–14:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:6\">2CH 16:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:1-Neh4:3\">NEH 4:1–4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:10\">ISA 9:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11\">AMO 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Boundary stones</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:14\">DEU 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:17\">DEU 27:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:2\">JOB 24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:28\">PRO 22:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:10-Prov23:11\">PRO 23:10–23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:10\">HOS 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Stones covering openings</h2>\n<h3>Wells</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:1-Gen29:10\">GEN 29:1–29:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The lions' den</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:16-Dan6:17\">DAN 6:16–6:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Tombs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:42-Mark15:46\">MRK 15:42–15:46</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57-Matt27:60\">MAT 27:57–27:60</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:62-Matt28:4\">MAT 27:62–28:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:5\">MRK 16:1–16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:3\">LUK 24:1–24:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:38-John11:44\">JHN 11:38–11:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1\">JHN 20:1</a></p>\n<h2>Stone jars</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:19\">EXO 7:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:1-John2:10\">JHN 2:1–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Stones as weapons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:16\">JDG 20:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:17\">NUM 35:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:38-1Sam17:50\">1SA 17:38–17:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:2\">1CH 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:15\">2CH 26:15</a></p>\n<h2>Stones in religious use</h2>\n<h3>Stone altars</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:24-Exod20:26\">EXO 20:24–20:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:1-Deut27:8\">DEU 27:1–27:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:30-Josh8:32\">JOS 8:30–8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:30-1Kgs18:38\">1KI 18:30–18:38</a></p>\n<h3>Memorial stones</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:12\">1SA 7:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:10-Gen28:22\">GEN 28:10–28:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:43-Gen31:53\">GEN 31:43–31:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:14-Gen35:15\">GEN 35:14–35:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:3-Exod24:4\">EXO 24:3–24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:1-Deut27:8\">DEU 27:1–27:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:1-Josh4:24\">JOS 4:1–4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:26-Josh24:27\">JOS 24:26–24:27</a></p>\n<h3>Ten Commandments written on stone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:18\">EXO 31:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:12\">EXO 24:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:1-Exod34:4\">EXO 34:1–34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:13\">DEU 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:22\">DEU 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:9-Deut9:11\">DEU 9:9–9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:1-Deut10:3\">DEU 10:1–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:9\">1KI 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:3-Heb9:4\">HEB 9:3–9:4</a></p>\n<h3>Sacred stones</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22-1Kgs14:23\">1KI 14:22–14:23</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:24\">EXO 23:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:13\">EXO 34:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:5\">DEU 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:3\">DEU 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:22\">DEU 16:22</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:2\">2KI 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:26-2Kgs10:27\">2KI 10:26–10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:10\">2KI 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4\">2KI 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:14\">2KI 23:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:1\">2CH 31:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:9\">ISA 27:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:4\">HOS 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:1-Hos10:2\">HOS 10:1–10:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:13\">MIC 5:13</a></p>\n<h3>Stone idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:19\">HAB 2:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:28\">DEU 4:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:36\">DEU 28:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:64\">DEU 28:64</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:17\">DEU 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:18\">2KI 19:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:19\">ISA 37:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:29\">ACT 17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20\">REV 9:20</a></p>\n<h2>Stonecutters and stonemasons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:15\">1KI 5:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:2\">2CH 2:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:11-2Kgs12:12\">2KI 12:11–12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:2\">1CH 22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:15\">1CH 22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:18\">2CH 2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Death by stoning</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:10-Lev24:16\">LEV 24:10–24:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:12-Exod19:13\">EXO 19:12–19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:28-Exod21:32\">EXO 21:28–21:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:2\">LEV 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:27\">LEV 20:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:32-Num15:36\">NUM 15:32–15:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:6-Deut13:11\">DEU 13:6–13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:2-Deut17:5\">DEU 17:2–17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:25\">JOS 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:18\">1KI 12:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:18\">2CH 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1-1Kgs21:13\">1KI 21:1–21:13</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:33-1Kgs21:35\">21:33–21:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34\">LUK 13:34</a>ACT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:54-Luke7:60\">7:54–7:60</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19\">ACT 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:25\">2CO 11:25</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ described as a stone</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:4–2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42-Matt21:44\">MAT 21:42–21:44</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10-Mark12:11\">MRK 12:10–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17-Luke20:18\">LUK 20:17–20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8-Acts4:12\">ACT 4:8–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:33\">ROM 9:33</a></p>\n<h2>Believers described as living stones</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical references to stones</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26\">EZK 36:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:5\">EXO 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:15-Exod15:16\">EXO 15:15–15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:15\">2CH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:27\">2CH 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:11\">NEH 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:12\">JOB 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:29-Job38:30\">JOB 38:29–38:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:9\">EZK 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:19\">EZK 11:19</a></p>",
